				<h4>Seamlessly Connecting <br>Students with Mentors</h4>
			
			</div>
			
			<div class="right-img">
			
				<img src="assets/imuadisplay-right.png" alt="Imua Student Screen">
			
			</div>

		</div><!-- /topper -->
	
		<div class="content">
		
			<div class="track-progress clear">
							
				<div class="scholar-chart">
				
					<img src="assets/hoku-scholar1.png" alt="An example Hoku Scholar">
				
				</div>
				
				<div class="text">
					<div class="inner">
					
						<h4>Tracking your progress to college-ready</h4>
						<p>The path to becoming college-ready begins in middle school. It spans multiple dimensions of student growth, including academic performance, community involvement, extracurricular leadership, professional development, and test preparation. IMUA provides students every semester with milestones in each performance category and feedback on their progress of becoming holistically prepared for college.</p>
					
					</div>
				
				</div>
			
			</div> <!-- /progress -->
			
			<div class="communication clear">
			
				<div class="text">
				
					<div class="inner">
					
						<h4>Powerful Communication</h4>
